staff_statistics.description_chinese: Record show what you do for tribe. Party watch. Good for all. Remember, what you do show how much you care for future.
staff_statistics.footer: You help OP-FW grow. OP-Framework sees your work, makes us strong. Team make things happen. Work hard, do great. Glory to OP-FW!
staff_statistics.footer_chinese: You show loyalty to Party. System sees your work, makes us strong. Follow rules, keep peace. Watchful, we prosper. Glory to CCP!
staff_statistics.level_0_description: You walk staff path, but power sleep and not formed. Learn from wise whispers, see realm energy swirl. Greatness seeds in hand, wait for you to take.
staff_statistics.level_10_description: Stories tell of your rise, light that calms wild storms. Staff power shines everywhere, unite those you guard. At top of mortal power, you shape realm fate with strong words.
staff_statistics.level_1_description: First staff magic glow in hand, help with small server problems. Ready to calm fights, stop unrest, show worth. Magic link grows with each help call, promise more power.
staff_statistics.level_2_description: Embrace small currents shape server. You juggle reports, steps with skill. Chaos tremble. You calm, solve fast. Actions weave you in realm, strong resolve keep peace.
staff_statistics.level_3_description: You command magic wards, banish spells keep server calm. Troublemakers stopped by you. Staff glow with power. Shadows come, you stay strong, change chaos to win.
staff_statistics.level_4_description: From dark corners, you watch. See mischief flicker, stop it fast. You swift, precise. No foe stay long. Order, chaos safe under your watch.
staff_statistics.level_5_description: Stars guide you, keep peace with grace. Realm trust you, stop fight, help others. Each day, you grow strong with stars, light way for all.
staff_statistics.level_6_description: Staff strong. Push bad things away fast. People fear name. You fair when use power.
staff_statistics.level_7_description: Shine bright, lead strong. Stop trouble quick. Stories of you make others follow. Keep place safe.
staff_statistics.level_8_description: Walk between light and dark. See chaos before it happens. Use skill to keep peace. All live together good.
staff_statistics.level_9_description: Win many fights. Smart and fair. Bad ones disappear. Your rule strong, place stays tough.
staff_statistics.title: Staff stats
